Mission

The mission of ULMS-YP is to support the National Urban League's movement through volunteerism, philanthropy, and membership development. We accomplish this by supporting our local affiliate, The Urban League of Metropolitan Seattle, providing a forum for the development of young professionals and engagement of the greater Seattle area youth.

Donate

All donations are tax deductable and go toward crafting our wonderful events throughout the year.

What we stand for

Our Focus

As an extrension of the ULMS, the Young Professionals are here to EMPOWER the surrounding communites in the following areas:

Economic Empowerment

Providing strategies that will financially help stabilize communities that have historically been locked out and ignored in the wealth conversation.

Social Justice

Representation for the ostracized and voices for the silenced. SULYP in conjuction will work towards creating equity in all facets of life.

Civic Engagement

Engaging, rather than waiting to be engaged.

Youth Development

Working to create pipelines of success from Pre-K to Post Grad. SULYP is dedicated to the continual growth, development, and opoportunities for those working towards their goals.

Health & Quality of Life

Health is wealth and peace of mind is priceless. SULYP is dedicated to bring you programming that will increase the holistic health statusL: Mind, Body, Spirit.
